    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Man on the Block&quot; is a game where you control a man and jump down blocks that serve as scaffolding. Points are added each time you land on a block, so try to land on as many blocks as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once a block leaves your feet, it disappears, so you can't return to the same block again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to go around three stages filled with disappearing blocks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How many points can you earn in 3 laps?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, you can easily retry as many times as you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim to get the highest points by repeating the game over and over again.</p>",
